item.description:
Hi Incubators,

Come on out this week for a birthday party incubator!!! It's Nikki's big day so come on out and have some laughs with us. For those that don't know Nikki, she has helped out a lot as an organizer and before that she was my right hand lady helping out with the group like welcoming you all online when you first join. She is also usually the first person there every week so she rocks!

Bring a smile, a friend, and come for a celebration and for lots of Improv. We will be playing a ton on Nikki's favorite games.

And if you haven't met her or been to an incubator before, it's a perfect time to meet her and start incubating.

Remember no I prove experience required.

Cheers,

Jason
item.name: Nikki's Birthday Incubator!!!
